features: FRAMED & READY TO HANG – Hand made within the UK. The canvas is stretched tightly over a sturdy 30mm deep frame so the print can be hung upon the wall with ease.
HIGH-QUALITY FINISH – We use the highest quality inks to ensure the colours are rich, vibrant and fadeproof. The canvas material is also resistant to UV rays, finger marks and moisture.
SHIPPING – The picture is shipped to your home or office swiftly by a reputable U.K. based courier.
30 DAY GUARANTEE – We are confident you will love your print, but if you wish to return it we offer a 30-day no quibble returns policy.
description: Do you want to bring colour and style into your home while expressing your taste and personality? If so, decorate your walls with our canvas wall art. We offer a wide range of designs, allowing you to find the perfect print to complement your decor. The canvas material is hand-stretched over a 30 mm deep frame and coated with a Satin Giclee Varnish, shielding the print from UV rays, fingerprints, moisture, and stains and scratches. As a result, the colours of the artwork will remain rich and vibrant for years to come! Here at Big Box Art, we strive for perfection, so each canvas is thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our quality standards. Once dispatched, it is swiftly delivered via courier, arriving at your door ready to hang - right out of the box!
